<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 5 (Asbel) - Start</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>アスベル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Asbel</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>シェリア</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Cheria</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>やはりカレーは甘口が最高だ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Sweet curry really is the best!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>相変わらず、子どもっぽい趣味ね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The same childish taste as always, huh.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ちがうぞ、シェリア。
大人になって初めてわかる
本当の甘口というものがあるんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's not it, Cheria. There's a real sweetness
you only understand once you become an adult.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……たぶん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Probably.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それで今度はなにを守りたいの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So what is you're going to protect this time?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>この先にいるカイウスは
マーボーカレーが好きらしいんだ。
おかしいと思わないか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Caius, up ahead there, seems to like
mabo curry. Don't you find that odd?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>マーボーカレーが好きな事が？
別段おかしいとは思わないけど……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Liking mabo curry? I don't think anything
is particularly odd about that...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ちがう！
マーボーカレーを甘口にしないなんて
おかしいと思わないか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No! Don't you think it's just odd
to not have curry be sweet?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……そこなの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...You think so?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>俺は彼のマーボーカレー好きを
甘口カレー好きに変えてやりたい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I want to change his liking for
mabo curry to liking sweet curry!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>守りたいんだ、甘口カレーを！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I want to protect it! The sweet curry!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それはむしろ……マーボーカレーを
攻めてるんじゃない？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Isn't that more like... attacking mabo curry?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
